{
  "stem": "5911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now came the worst time, because we didn't want to go to Lithuania, because we had-- we were in a camp with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were treating us very nicely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do we do to run away?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took a long time, and I suppose a lot of courage to travel at night and get up again on trains as displaced persons to cross the border, the Russian border, into the-- into the American side.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they had American sides, the Russian side, to-- into the Allied side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just my mother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We latched on some other people were too that wanted, but it had to be on a very QT.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had to be the quietest thing, because we wanted to get to the American side to see who survived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that my mother's family, that the small towns were wiped out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That we knew right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had hope, because my father's friend said, we had hope.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father being very strong, will survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If we survived, he survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went from place to place until we decided to go, as I said before, on the American side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Polish-- Polish places.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we crossed the border, and we got into Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That I remember, getting into Lodz, because that was-- again, I can't-- you can't measure your life being in a traumatic situation living through what I went through.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess that was the worst time-- when I went to Lodz, and I found out that my father didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think, like to say now in this vernacular, I lost my cool.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went completely berserk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there wasn't any counselors or anybody to give a hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I suppose, again, my will to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
